{"code": 0, "data": {"allow_search": true, "attention": false, "author_title": null, "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "comments": [{"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 63568, "create_time": 1648779344, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "“转弯让直行”听说过没🍉\n电动车一方是超速、路口不减速，自行车一方是路口转弯不观察、转弯不打手势，我觉得都有责任，如果交警来，未必认定电动车全责", "timestamp": 1648779344}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 63569, "create_time": 1648779578, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Alice: 我没描述好，其实是这样的，这大叔从紫荆公寓往南走，女生往C楼拐，女生已经拐到对侧车道了，电动车由于速度过快（因为我和一众人正在向南车道上行驶）避让向南行驶的车，然后开往对侧车道，随即相撞", "timestamp": 1648779578}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 63573, "create_time": 1648779941, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "我还是没看懂，大叔北向南，女生北向东，大叔避让的车北向南，你和一众人也是北向南？大叔是在超车还是在避让……？", "timestamp": 1648779941}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 63574, "create_time": 1648779963, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "[![qhYBdg.jpg](https://s1.ax1x.com/2022/04/01/qhYBdg.jpg)](https://imgtu.com/i/qhYBdg)", "timestamp": 1648779963}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 63578, "create_time": 1648780058, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Alice: 哦应该是超车🤔", "timestamp": 1648780058}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 63579, "create_time": 1648780144, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "这么一想应该是超车，我一开始还以为是他停不住了，所以才以为是避让（可能这个表达也有问题），不过对侧车道超车也不合规吧", "timestamp": 1648780144}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 63582, "create_time": 1648780241, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "Re 洞主: 如果地上的线是虚线，在保证安全的前提下，是可以借对向车道超车的。但本案显然没有保证安全，我认可电动车全责", "timestamp": 1648780241}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 63584, "create_time": 1648780319, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "Re 洞主: 如果是“停不住了”，那是后车没有保持安全车距，这是另一条规则，追尾后车全责", "timestamp": 1648780319}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 63586, "create_time": 1648780431, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 2, "text": "Re Alice: 校园内也规章说事，我天天逆行是不是要被罚款？", "timestamp": 1648780431}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 63590, "create_time": 1648780880, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Bob: 啊？？", "timestamp": 1648780880}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 63593, "create_time": 1648780997, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "Re Bob: 不出事故就没事，出了事故如果对方报警，你要承担责任", "timestamp": 1648780997}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 63596, "create_time": 1648781528, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "《道路交通安全法》：\n>“道路”，是指公路、城市道路和虽在单位管辖范围但允许社会机动车通行的地方，包括广场、公共停车场等用于公众通行的场所。\n\n>车辆在道路以外通行时发生的事故，公安机关交通管理部门接到报案的，参照本法有关规定办理。", "timestamp": 1648781528}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 63684, "create_time": 1648792837, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 3, "text": "Re 洞主: 这种情况挺容易撞上的，因为超车的人不知道前车要转弯，转弯的也很少转头看", "timestamp": 1648792837}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 63685, "create_time": 1648792895, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 3, "text": "我之前也这样挡过后车。反正转弯路口的时候还想着超车都多少沾点", "timestamp": 1648792895}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 63750, "create_time": 1648798850, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 4, "text": "前车拐弯的时候示意一下或者回头看看，后车在路口就不超车可能就没事了，双方都有责任", "timestamp": 1648798850}], "create_time": 1648779092, "cw": null, "hot_score": null, "is_blocked": false, "is_reported": null, "is_tmp": false, "last_comment_time": 1648798850, "likenum": 6, "n_attentions": 6, "n_comments": 15, "pid": 23431, "poll": null, "reply": 15, "text": "学堂路紫金公寓一侧发生车祸，一个大叔骑电动车速度极快，正碰上一位女生骑车往C楼方向拐弯（速度极慢），大叔撞上女生单车侧面，两人倒地！\n不知道现在情况如何，dz赶着上课\n我的观点：电动车主全责，那一下真的猛，女生的腿得骨折；电动车主在路口还不减速，发现时已经来不及，只有时间大吼一声“诶”，然后两车即相撞，一切在电光火石之间", "timestamp": 1648779092}}